  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a tagine or large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic; sauté until soft (about 3 minutes).",
    "Stir in smoked paprika and red bell pepper; cook for 1 minute to release flavor.",
    "Add cherry tomatoes, chickpeas, and cilantro; mix gently.",
    "Simmer for 10 minutes until tomatoes are tender and flavors blend.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste."
